{"type":"info-page","slug":"mic/cgi/search","journal":"mic","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/mic/cgi/search","title":"Microbiology -- Search Result","bodyHtml":"<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"></a>\n        <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH RESULT</font></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\">\n        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#000000\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <br>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <p><strong><font face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" size=\"+1\" color=\"#003399\">There was a problem with our search system</font></strong></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">The most common cause of this type of problem is incorrectly specified author names in search arguments.</font></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Author names must be specified in the form of LastName, FirstInitial, as in Smith, R.</strong></font></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Additional punctuation, initials, or full first names will cause an error.</font></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Other common causes of this type of problem involve improper use of punctuation, such as semi-colons or unmatched parentheses.</font></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">If neither of the explanation above applies to your search, this may be a temporary problem. However, if you get this error only for certain searches, or over a period of time, please <a href=\"/mic/cgi/feedback\">let us know</a> what your search was, so that we can fix it. Please include your <em>exact</em> search.</font></p>\n  <p><font size=\"-1\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">To rephrase your existing search criteria, press the \"Back\" button on your browser, or you can <a href=\"/mic/search.dtl\">enter a new search</a>.</font></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/mic/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH RESULT</font></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"375\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">INT J SYST EVOL MICROBIOL</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">MICROBIOLOGY</font></td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/vir/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J GEN VIROL</font></a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">J MED MICROBIOL</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\" colspan=\"2\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ALL SGM JOURNALS</font></a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table><font size=\"-1\"><strong><a target=\"_top\" href=\"/mic/misc/terms.shtml\">Copyright © 2004 Society for General Microbiology.</a></strong></font>"}